{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc9d4cbb3-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s390zz"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"390zz"},"text":"§ 390zz.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reporting","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any contracting entity subject to the ownership or pricing limitations of Federal reclamation law shall compile and maintain such records and information as the Secretary deems reasonably necessary to implement this subchapter and Federal reclamation law. On a date set by the Secretary following ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-12"},"text":"October 12, 1982","children":[],"tail":", and annually thereafter, every such contracting entity shall provide in a form suitable to the Secretary such reports on the above matters as the Secretary may require."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc9d4cbb4-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/293/tII/s228"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–293, title II, § 228","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1274"},"text":"96 Stat. 1274","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc9d4cbb5-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc9d4cbb6-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idc9d4cbb7-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Federal reclamation law, referred to in text, is defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s390aa"},"text":"section 390aa of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
